@CarbonDogma Having said that, my time in esports has taught me seeding is a thankless task that will always piss someone off, and I'm eternally grateful its not my job.

Either way, you understand the point. Critics not having solutions doesn't invalidate their criticism as a rule, or prove a solution/better method doesn't exist.
